        Passa a trovarci,<br />
        <span class="italic text-[rgb(185,140,75)]">ti aspettiamo!</span>
      </h2>
      <div
        class="space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-[rgb(12,12,12)]/70 leading-relaxed gallery-animate"
        data-animation="fade-up"
        data-delay="100"
